WEBVTT

00:00.022 --> 00:01.287
<i>Previously on Boston Legal…</i>

00:01.287 --> 00:03.022
I believe Rachel's using again.

00:03.022 --> 00:04.656
What proof do you have?

00:04.691 --> 00:06.291
She asked to borrow $40.

00:06.292 --> 00:09.492
Crystal meth users live
their lives in $40-increments.

00:09.492 --> 00:12.186
I want you to find out
if my daughter is using drugs again.

00:12.186 --> 00:13.525
What time do you get off work?

00:13.525 --> 00:15.831
She's sweet, beautiful,
nothing rattles her.

00:15.831 --> 00:17.498
Even when she lost her ATM card.

00:17.498 --> 00:18.486
What are you talking about?

00:18.486 --> 00:21.626
Rachel lost her ATM card,
so I loaned her 40 bucks.

00:21.661 --> 00:23.379
You have a child. A child!

00:23.414 --> 00:24.537
You bastard.

00:24.572 --> 00:25.772
I'm helping Melissa,

00:25.806 --> 00:28.849
who seems to have fallen
into a black hole of debt.

00:28.849 --> 00:30.812
Very black.

